#Constants explained

#The defenition of a variable is
#A named location
#In a computers memory
#that stores a value
#the value can change

#The defenition of a CONSTANT is:
#A named location
#in a computers memory
#that stores a value
#the value SHOULD NOT be changed
#it is written in all capital letters

#Here is an example of a CONSTANT
FREETHROW = 1
DUNKSHOT = 2
PI = 3.141
THREEPOINTER = 3
numberOFfouls = 0 # this is a variable
